title: OXFORD HANDBOOK OF MENTAL HEALTH NURSING
description: Author: Patrick Callaghan, Catherine Gamble Edition: 2 edition Publication Date: November 24, 2015 Publisher: Oxford University Press ISBN-10: 0198703856 ISBN-13: 978-0198703853 Pages: 432 pages Format: pdf Size: 2.0M --- Fully revised for its second edition, the Oxford Handbook of Mental Health Nursing is the indispensable resource for all those caring for patients with mental health problems. Practical, concise, and up-to-date with the latest guidelines, practice, and initiatives, this handbook is designed to allow essential information to be quickly accessible to nurses in a busy clinical setting. --- http://dlfeb.com/book/oxford-handbook-of-mental-health-nursing-oxford-handbooks-in-nursing/
